<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That's so embarrassing.</font>

472
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like you've read the Suzuki
Kaitai Shinsho, or dissected me like a fish.</font>

473
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Fall is here!</font>

474
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the summer, it's so muggy
 after the rain stops,</font>

475
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but when it rains closer to autumn, 
it really changes the air, doesn't it?</font>

476
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it does.</font>

477
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When our middle school culture festival 
ended, the temperature was like this,</font>

478
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so now, whenever I feel this, like, 
whoosh of air changing,</font>

479
00:21:37,530 --> 00:21:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always think, "Ah, the culture festival 
is done for this year, too."</font>

480
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like I'll probably say 
the same thing next year, too.</font>

481
00:21:48,290 --> 00:21:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think probably...</font>

482
00:21:50,660 --> 00:21:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>From now on, whenever I feel 
this same atmosphere...</i></font>

483
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll remember today.</font>

484
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's...</font>

485
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you say something like that to me...</font>

486
00:22:10,850 --> 00:22:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then I'll end up the same way!</font>

487
00:22:14,150 --> 00:22:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that bad?</font>

488
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good!</font>

489
00:22:16,730 --> 00:22:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miyu has a boyfriend?</font>

